  "title": "Night Shift Warehouse Assistant (Up to $2720 / 4 Days / Clementi)",
  "description": "<p>Job Title: Night Shift Warehouse Assistant (ID5094)<br />Location: Clementi<br />Working Hours: Work 4 days 8.30pm – 8.30am (12 Hours Night Shift)<br />Salary: up to $2720<br /><br />Job Description:<br />• Handle inbound and outbound process.<br />• Prepare daily can’t view reports.<br />• Perform daily inventory cycle count.<br />• Communicate with driver for urgent delivery.<br />• Arrange red rush if activated.<br />• Arrange ADHOC collection if any urgent request by engineers or call management.<br />• Arrange manual release if HPE approve.<br />• Manage EXPO order if system under maintenance.<br />• Check stock availability using Easitool website.<br />• Other ad-hoc operation duties as assigned.<br />• Job training provided.<br /><br />Requirement:<br />• Minimum N-Level<br />• At least 1–2 years of relevant experience<br />• Must be able to work on weekend and public holidays.<br />• Physically fit, healthy and able to carry heavy parts.<br />• Able to work as a team and support each other.</p>",
